Bhavana Public School, Degaon, established in the year 2003, led by highly qualified and dedicated teachers from Kerala, enjoys the pride of place in the educational sphere of Vidarbha region. The school recognizes the fact that the great advances in science and technology and the rapid expansion of knowledge, it has become imperative that learning becomes specific and well-defined to enable students to acquire the professional knowledge required to survive in this increasing competitive world.
